The paper focuses on user response prediction, which is a common problem in information retrieval and filtering scenarios such as recommender systems and web search. The data is mostly in a multi-field categorical format, which suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep neural networks and feature engineering also supports the likelihood of belonging to these sub-categories.
